# Vibe Coding

When this rule applies (files under `VibeCoding/` are in context):

1. Follow the project skill **vibe-coding-workflow** (`.cursor/skills/vibe-coding-workflow/SKILL.md`): Clarify → write/update `{TaskName}_Plan.md` → implement while appending `{TaskName}_Progress.md`.
2. Do not skip clarification for new tasks unless the user explicitly waives it.
3. Implementation changes must remain traceable in `_Progress.md` after each completed plan step or coherent batch of work.
4. If implementation deviates from `{TaskName}_Plan.md`, apply the deviation handling protocol in the skill before continuing.
